This button is inspired by [url=http://custombuttons.sourceforge.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=2&t=3732]a post[/url] by [b]BarbieBarb[/b] and a site posted in that post by [b]srazzano[/b]. It allows you to generate formatted text to be used on places where it is not possible to give the text any kind of style and/or to apply styles not available. The [i]text formatting[/i] is achieved by replacing each character in a word/sentence for an [url=http://unicode-table.com/en/][b]Unicode[/b][/url] character representing that [i]stylized[/i] character. Almost all functions used by this button are extracted from [url=http://lingojam.com/]LingoJam[/url], where hundreds of translators/conversors/stylers are available.

