[size=150][b]Usage[/b][/size]
[list]
[*] Click this button to open [b]Formatted Text Generator[/b] main window.
[*] Type or paste or load from a file some text on the textbox.
[*] Select the text to which you want to apply a style.
[*] Click on any button from the [b]Bookmarks[/b] section or any menu item from the [b]Styles menus[/b] section to apply a style.[/list]

